name: Shintaro Kago - Card #11
description:
Shintaro Kago - Card #11
This is a gift card to collectors and friends.
It is an authorized tribute to the work of Japanese mangaka "Shintaro Kago". I was able to contact him and he authorized the existence of this work created by me.
This card has no use in the "Rude World Cup". It is only an important thank you to all those who accompany my way.
Feel free to give away, sell or burn this object if you wish. 
Thank you very much for everything, Matias La Plata.
